Dialogue: 100,0:03:10.00,0:03:12.46,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}什么？你开玩笑吧\N{\fnArial\fs48}What? You've got to be joking.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:13.35,0:03:15.00,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你知道我什么时候在开玩笑\N{\fnArial\fs48}You'll know when I'm joking.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:17.13,0:03:18.51,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我和史蒂文可以跟她去\N{\fnArial\fs48}Me and Steven can go with her.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:19.66,0:03:21.03,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}对，我们会盯着她的\N{\fnArial\fs48}Yeah, we'll keep an eye on her.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:21.91,0:03:24.33,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}准许，让她老实点，紫晶\N{\fnArial\fs48}Approved. Keep her in line, Amethyst.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:24.64,0:03:25.80,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}收到！\N{\fnArial\fs48}You got it!
Dialogue: 100,0:03:27.48,0:03:29.60,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}记录日期-7-1-1-2\N{\fnArial\fs48}Log date 7-1-1-2.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:29.62,0:03:32.17,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}那个紫晶和那个史蒂文自愿\N{\fnArial\fs48}The Amethyst and the Steven have volunteered
Dialogue: 100,0:03:32.17,0:03:34.28,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}帮助我拆解这个第一代钻头\N{\fnArial\fs48}to help me dismantle this era-one drill.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:34.66,0:03:36.77,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}这在文体上非常不愉快\N{\fnArial\fs48}How stylistically displeasing.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:36.77,0:03:38.75,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}新一点的有更美观的抛光处理\N{\fnArial\fs48}The newer ones have a nicer finish.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:39.13,0:03:40.98,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你在制造更多的书呆子日志吗？\N{\fnArial\fs48}You making more nerd notes?
Dialogue: 100,0:03:41.55,0:03:43.35,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}什么是...书呆子？\N{\fnArial\fs48}What is...Nerd?
Dialogue: 100,0:03:45.24,0:03:46.92,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你能造个句吗？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Can you use it in a sentence?
Dialogue: 100,0:03:47.88,0:03:48.51,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}书呆子-\N{\fnArial\fs48}Nerd --
Dialogue: 100,0:03:48.82,0:03:50.19,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你是个，书呆子\N{\fnArial\fs48}you are a nerd.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:52.26,0:03:54.15,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}紫晶，别说了\N{\fnArial\fs48}Amethyst, cut that out.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:54.64,0:03:56.95,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}正如你所见，这颗星球非常烦人，\N{\fnArial\fs48}As you can see, this planet is annoying,
Dialogue: 100,0:03:56.95,0:03:58.75,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}每个事物都如此\N{\fnArial\fs48}and everything is annoying.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:58.97,0:04:02.37,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}在这个星球所有的罪行中包含紫晶需要\N{\fnArial\fs48}Amongst its transgressions is the need for the Amethyst
Dialogue: 100,0:04:02.37,0:04:04.20,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}向永融体寻求许可\N{\fnArial\fs48}to ask permission from the permafusion.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:04.42,0:04:06.75,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}永融体？那是你对石榴的称呼吗？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Permafusion? Is that what you call Garnet?
Dialogue: 100,0:04:06.97,0:04:08.93,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我可以称呼她很多名字\N{\fnArial\fs48}I could call her lots of things.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:09.15,0:04:12.26,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我可以称呼她“两个东西”-“两个草包”！\N{\fnArial\fs48}I could call her two things -- two clods!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:13.02,0:04:15.84,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}四处游荡，好似她是一个草包一样\N{\fnArial\fs48}Walking around like she's one clod.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:17.95,0:04:19.17,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}这有什么不对吗？\N{\fnArial\fs48}What's wrong with that?
Dialogue: 100,0:04:19.88,0:04:21.02,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}她又没在战斗！\N{\fnArial\fs48}She's not even fighting!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:21.02,0:04:23.51,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}她在-你懂的-她只是在-你懂的，像个...\N{\fnArial\fs48}She's -- you know, she's just, you know, like a...
Dialogue: 100,0:04:25.02,0:04:25.73,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你懂的！\N{\fnArial\fs48}You know!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:31.02,0:04:32.97,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你真算个宝石人啊，“橄榄”\N{\fnArial\fs48}You're a real gem, "Perry."
Dialogue: 100,0:04:33.46,0:04:35.90,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}是的，我是个，宝石人\N{\fnArial\fs48}Yes. I am. A gem.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:36.17,0:04:38.26,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}好吧，好吧，来说说史蒂文吧\N{\fnArial\fs48}Okay, okay. Do Steven next.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:38.53,0:04:40.11,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}史蒂文有什么古怪的吗？\N{\fnArial\fs48}What's weird about Steven?
Dialogue: 100,0:04:40.37,0:04:41.88,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我该从何说起呢？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Where do I even begin?
Dialogue: 100,0:04:42.11,0:04:44.15,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}他算某种混血弃儿\N{\fnArial\fs48}He's some sort of hybrid abomination.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:44.40,0:04:46.37,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我甚至都无法理解他是如何维持生命的\N{\fnArial\fs48}I don't even understand how he functions.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:46.37,0:04:48.44,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}他有机的那部分消耗了太多能量\N{\fnArial\fs48}His organic half consumes so much energy
Dialogue: 100,0:04:48.44,0:04:49.97,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}让他不得不频繁进食，\N{\fnArial\fs48}that he has to constantly feed,
Dialogue: 100,0:04:49.97,0:04:52.04,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}并且他得花大把时间排泄，\N{\fnArial\fs48}and he spends so much time expelling
Dialogue: 100,0:04:52.40,0:04:55.11,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}以致有单独的房间做这件事\N{\fnArial\fs48}that he has a whole room dedicated to it.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:55.84,0:04:57.73,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}呃，不，别的东西啊-\N{\fnArial\fs48}Uh, no, something else --
Dialogue: 100,0:04:57.73,0:04:58.99,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}说点别的东西啊！\N{\fnArial\fs48}talk about something else!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:05.08,0:05:07.31,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}最奇怪的是，紫晶，\N{\fnArial\fs48}The strangest thing is, Amethyst,
Dialogue: 100,0:05:07.46,0:05:09.73,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你以为你得听她们的\N{\fnArial\fs48}you think you have to listen to them.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:11.42,0:05:13.57,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你才是那个应该指挥的人\N{\fnArial\fs48}You're the one who should be in charge!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:13.77,0:05:14.24,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}哈！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Ha!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:14.66,0:05:16.68,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}这是你目前最好的段子了！\N{\fnArial\fs48}That's your best joke yet.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:16.68,0:05:17.97,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}不，真的\N{\fnArial\fs48}No, really.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:17.97,0:05:19.31,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}珍珠是个珍珠\N{\fnArial\fs48}Pearl is a Pearl.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:19.31,0:05:20.95,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}石榴是个融合体\N{\fnArial\fs48}Garnet is a fusion.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:21.13,0:05:23.62,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我都猜不到他存在的目的\N{\fnArial\fs48}I don't even know what he's supposed to be.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:23.77,0:05:24.68,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}嘿！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Hey!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:24.80,0:05:28.29,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你是水晶战士中唯一一个真正的宝石人\N{\fnArial\fs48}You're the only Crystal Gem that's actually a gem.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:31.26,0:05:31.77,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}什么？\N{\fnArial\fs48}What?
Dialogue: 100,0:05:32.31,0:05:33.97,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你比队里其他的人的等级都要高\N{\fnArial\fs48}You outrank everyone on your team.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:34.28,0:05:35.77,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}她们该听你的才对\N{\fnArial\fs48}They should be listening to you.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:36.11,0:05:38.95,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你是个强壮的，独立的，完全正常的战士，\N{\fnArial\fs48}You're a strong, singular, fully functional soldier,
Dialogue: 100,0:05:39.15,0:05:40.88,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}即使实际上你是有缺陷的\N{\fnArial\fs48}despite the fact that you're defective.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:42.00,0:05:42.77,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}缺陷？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Defective?
Dialogue: 100,0:05:43.20,0:05:44.97,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}啊，当然，你太挫了\N{\fnArial\fs48}Well, sure. You're small.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:45.37,0:05:46.22,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}所以？\N{\fnArial\fs48}So?
Dialogue: 100,0:05:46.73,0:05:48.31,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}其实，你不该是这样的\N{\fnArial\fs48}Well, you're not supposed to be.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:48.68,0:05:50.08,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}等下，等等\N{\fnArial\fs48}Hold on. Wait, wait.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:50.64,0:05:52.22,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我猜猜，这-\N{\fnArial\fs48}Let me guess. This --
Dialogue: 100,0:05:53.02,0:05:54.66,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}这是你出生的洞\N{\fnArial\fs48}this is the hole you came out of.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:55.26,0:05:57.35,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}太小，太低\N{\fnArial\fs48}Too small, too low,
Dialogue: 100,0:05:57.57,0:05:59.88,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}出口的痕迹看起来相比其他洞\N{\fnArial\fs48}the exit marks look about 500 years newer
Dialogue: 100,0:05:59.88,0:06:01.68,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}晚了500年左右，嗯\N{\fnArial\fs48}than every other hole. Hmm.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:01.97,0:06:03.97,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你出来的时候这里一定已经空了吧\N{\fnArial\fs48}This place must've been empty when you came out.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:04.40,0:06:07.17,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}难怪你不知道你该长成什么样子！\N{\fnArial\fs48}No wonder you have no idea what you're supposed to look like!
Dialogue: 100,0:06:07.57,0:06:08.77,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}橄榄石\N{\fnArial\fs48}Peridot.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:09.24,0:06:11.00,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我应该是什么样子？\N{\fnArial\fs48}What was I supposed to look like?
Dialogue: 100,0:06:11.26,0:06:12.82,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}首先，你是个石英\N{\fnArial\fs48}Well, you're a Quartz.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:13.20,0:06:15.64,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}石英是魁梧，忠诚的士兵\N{\fnArial\fs48}They're huge, loyal soldiers.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:15.88,0:06:20.48,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你应该再大上一倍，肩膀宽阔，令人生畏，\N{\fnArial\fs48}You should be twice your size, broad-shouldered, intimidating,
Dialogue: 100,0:06:20.48,0:06:23.01,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}但你只是在地里待了太长时间了\N{\fnArial\fs48}but you simply stayed in the ground too long.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:23.35,0:06:24.66,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你是说我是个错误吗？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Are you saying I'm wrong?
Dialogue: 100,0:06:26.26,0:06:27.97,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}“宝石学”上讲，没错\N{\fnArial\fs48}"Gemetically" speaking, yes.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:28.13,0:06:31.11,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}当你考虑这件事时，这真变得有趣啊\N{\fnArial\fs48}When you think about it, it's all so funny.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:32.60,0:06:33.37,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}紫晶\N{\fnArial\fs48}Amethyst.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:33.80,0:06:35.13,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}嘿，士兵，\N{\fnArial\fs48}Hey, soldier,
Dialogue: 100,0:06:35.33,0:06:37.77,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}也许你可以帮我拆下这块钻头\N{\fnArial\fs48}maybe you can help me get this hunk of drill off.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:41.22,0:06:43.06,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}瞧，看看！\N{\fnArial\fs48}See? Look at that!
Dialogue: 100,0:06:43.28,0:06:45.82,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你能完成正常的石英能做的所有事情\N{\fnArial\fs48}You can do everything a normal Quartz can do.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:46.06,0:06:49.06,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}让我们回去用这个糊珍珠一脸吧\N{\fnArial\fs48}Let's head back and shove this thing in Pearl's face.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:49.55,0:06:51.48,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}紫晶，你还好吗？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Amethyst, are you okay?
Dialogue: 100,0:06:51.88,0:06:53.13,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}不要担心\N{\fnArial\fs48}Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:53.80,0:06:56.04,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}哦！这真是太有爱了\N{\fnArial\fs48}Oh! It's lovely.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:56.26,0:06:57.08,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}考虑到我们将使用\N{\fnArial\fs48}To think we'd be using
Dialogue: 100,0:06:57.08,0:07:00.35,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}一开始引起这一切的技术来解决这一切-\N{\fnArial\fs48}the same technology that started all this to fix it --
Dialogue: 100,0:07:00.53,0:07:03.13,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}这个钻头真是纯嘲讽啊！\N{\fnArial\fs48}this drill is pure irony!
Dialogue: 100,0:07:03.37,0:07:05.20,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}实际上，它大部分是碳\N{\fnArial\fs48}Actually, it's mostly carbonite.
Dialogue: 500,0:07:03.37,0:07:05.20,Label Trans,,0,0,0,,{\fn隶书\fs48\c&H6C6F75&\bord0\shad0\pos(142,982)}钉子
Dialogue: 500,0:07:03.37,0:07:05.20,Label Trans,,0,0,0,,{\fn隶书\fs48\c&H6C6F75&\bord0\shad0\pos(224,920)}螺丝
Dialogue: 100,0:07:05.53,0:07:07.57,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}这会让它变得“碳讽”吗？（irony：铁的，讽刺性的；carbon:碳）\N{\fnArial\fs48}Would that make it "carbony"?
Dialogue: 100,0:07:08.77,0:07:10.16,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}哦，哦，哦！紫晶！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Oh, oh, oh! Amethyst!
Dialogue: 100,0:07:11.95,0:07:16.91,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}看这个-嗯-节奏性粉碎器！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Check out this -- hmm -- "rhythmatic" pulverizer.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:18.55,0:07:20.11,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}那真是太好笑了！我太幽默了！\N{\fnArial\fs48}That's funny. I'm so funny. 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:22.57,0:07:23.66,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你高兴就好\N{\fnArial\fs48}Whatever, dude.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:24.73,0:07:27.51,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}那不是正确的反应啊\N{\fnArial\fs48}That was the incorrect response.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:27.84,0:07:31.11,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}嘿，我做这些的时候紫晶没笑诶\N{\fnArial\fs48}Hey, Amethyst isn't laughing when I do these things.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:31.26,0:07:32.48,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}为什么她不笑出来？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Why isn't she laughing?
Dialogue: 100,0:07:32.93,0:07:35.72,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}橄榄石，你真的伤害了她的情感了\N{\fnArial\fs48}Peridot, you really hurt her feelings.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:36.37,0:07:36.82,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}什么？\N{\fnArial\fs48}What?
Dialogue: 100,0:07:37.44,0:07:39.37,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你在幼儿园时对她有点太过刻薄了\N{\fnArial\fs48}You were pretty mean to her at the kindergarten.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:39.71,0:07:41.66,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}刻薄？不可能\N{\fnArial\fs48}Mean? No way.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:41.95,0:07:45.06,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}那只是...酷，紫晶喜欢的\N{\fnArial\fs48}I was being...Cool. Amethyst loved it.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:45.42,0:07:47.88,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}她可能只是在告诉珍珠她现在有多快乐\N{\fnArial\fs48}She's probably telling the Pearl how much fun she had now.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:48.24,0:07:50.46,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}紫晶，嗨，嗨！嗨。紫晶！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Amethyst, hi, hi! Hi, Amethyst!
Dialogue: 100,0:07:52.55,0:07:54.50,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}她-她都不愿意看我\N{\fnArial\fs48}She -- she won't even look at me.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:54.88,0:07:57.82,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}这让我感觉很...渺小\N{\fnArial\fs48}It's making me feel... Smaller.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:58.22,0:08:00.73,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你感觉难受，那也是你让她感受到的\N{\fnArial\fs48}You feel bad. That's how you made her feel.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:02.22,0:08:04.24,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}谁在乎她感觉怎么样？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Who cares about how she feels?
Dialogue: 100,0:08:04.42,0:08:05.71,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}谁在乎你们中的任何一个？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Who cares about any of you?!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:05.95,0:08:07.02,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你们都只是石头而已，\N{\fnArial\fs48}You're all just rocks,
Dialogue: 100,0:08:07.02,0:08:09.75,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}拜倒在我的重力连接器下的红润的肮脏的土块\N{\fnArial\fs48}ruddy muddy clumps beneath my gravity connectors!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:12.11,0:08:14.28,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}她又一次莫名其妙的发飙了\N{\fnArial\fs48}Another one of her temper tantrums.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:14.53,0:08:16.77,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我很惊讶你们俩能从幼儿园正常的回来\N{\fnArial\fs48}I'm surprised you two made it back from the kindergarten
Dialogue: 100,0:08:16.77,0:08:18.35,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}而没把对方逼疯\N{\fnArial\fs48}without driving each other crazy.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:18.97,0:08:19.86,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}是啊\N{\fnArial\fs48}Yeah.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:22.31,0:08:23.17,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}这个小东西-\N{\fnArial\fs48}This little thing --
Dialogue: 100,0:08:23.17,0:08:24.91,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}啊啊！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Aah!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:28.04,0:08:29.48,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}上面的进展怎么样了？\N{\fnArial\fs48}How's everything going up there?
Dialogue: 100,0:08:29.77,0:08:31.33,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我很好，没什么出差错的\N{\fnArial\fs48}I'm fine. There's nothing wrong.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:31.33,0:08:32.82,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}所有事都非常顺利\N{\fnArial\fs48}Everything's fine. 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:33.60,0:08:35.57,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}啊！不不不不！停下！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Aah! No, no, no, no! Stop!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:35.80,0:08:36.40,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}橄榄石？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Peridot?
Dialogue: 100,0:08:40.42,0:08:41.11,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}面板！\N{\fnArial\fs48}The panel.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:43.28,0:08:45.35,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}喔！等等！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Whoa! Wait!
