Dialogue: 100,0:08:51.46,0:08:53.02,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}搞毛...啊！\N{\fnArial\fs48}What the...Aah!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:53.02,0:08:53.91,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}紫晶！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Amethyst! 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:57.84,0:08:58.53,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}啊！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Aah!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:04.60,0:09:06.86,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}没什么，一切都好\N{\fnArial\fs48}It's okay. Everything's okay.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:06.86,0:09:08.51,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}这只是个钻头（drill:钻头，演习）\N{\fnArial\fs48}It was just a drill.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:17.37,0:09:18.84,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}呃...橄榄石？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Uh...Peridot?
Dialogue: 100,0:09:19.11,0:09:21.35,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}啊！这只是个意外！我发誓！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Aah! It was an accident. I swear!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:21.66,0:09:23.13,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}嘿，别担心\N{\fnArial\fs48}Hey, don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:23.35,0:09:25.17,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我们知道你不是故意启动钻头的\N{\fnArial\fs48}We know you didn't mean to start the drill.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:26.22,0:09:28.91,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}呃，是的，那也只是个意外\N{\fnArial\fs48}Uh, yeah. And that was an accident, too.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:30.53,0:09:32.80,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我们才走了一秒钟，\N{\fnArial\fs48}We leave for one second,
Dialogue: 100,0:09:32.84,0:09:35.75,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}就出了乱子！\N{\fnArial\fs48}and everything goes off the rails!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:36.66,0:09:37.64,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我怪奶牛\N{\fnArial\fs48}I blame the cows.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:38.00,0:09:39.60,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}不，没什么，一切都好\N{\fnArial\fs48}No, it's fine. It's fine.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:40.08,0:09:42.41,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我们会将它重新制造的更强大，更好\N{\fnArial\fs48}We'll rebuild it stronger, better.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:42.88,0:09:44.31,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我们会加上安全带的 ！\N{\fnArial\fs48}We'll add seatbelts!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:46.57,0:09:47.44,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}啊！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Ah!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:47.88,0:09:50.46,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}嘿，你们还好吗？那真是惊险啊\N{\fnArial\fs48}Hey, are you all right? That was a close one.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:50.80,0:09:52.80,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}还好橄榄石救了你\N{\fnArial\fs48}It's a good thing Peridot was there to save you.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:54.22,0:09:56.15,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}当然，这是件好事\N{\fnArial\fs48}Yes, it is a good thing.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:59.66,0:10:01.46,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}听着，我，呃...\N{\fnArial\fs48}Listen. I, um...
Dialogue: 100,0:10:01.46,0:10:02.40,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}说出来啊\N{\fnArial\fs48}Just spit it out.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:03.31,0:10:04.02,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}啊！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Ugh!
Dialogue: 100,0:10:04.02,0:10:06.88,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}\为什么你们地球人就这么难交流？！N{\fnArial\fs48}Why are you earthlings so difficult?!
Dialogue: 100,0:10:07.88,0:10:10.00,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}记录日期-7-1-1-2\N{\fnArial\fs48}Log date 7-1-1-2.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:10.35,0:10:13.48,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}整个星球完全颠倒了\N{\fnArial\fs48}This entire planet is backwards.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:13.77,0:10:16.15,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}目前还没有任何一个正常的行为\N{\fnArial\fs48}There hasn't been one instance of correct behavior
Dialogue: 100,0:10:16.15,0:10:19.13,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}体现在水晶战士的身上\N{\fnArial\fs48}exhibited by any one of these crystal gems.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:19.44,0:10:21.62,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我得出结论-她们全部都是有缺陷的\N{\fnArial\fs48}I have concluded that they are all defective.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:22.64,0:10:23.77,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}但我也没好到哪去\N{\fnArial\fs48}But I am no better.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:24.05,0:10:25.31,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我的任务失败了，\N{\fnArial\fs48}I failed my mission,
Dialogue: 100,0:10:25.31,0:10:27.15,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}而现在我又与敌人共事，\N{\fnArial\fs48}and now I'm working with the enemy,
Dialogue: 100,0:10:27.15,0:10:29.04,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}但连这个我都做不好\N{\fnArial\fs48}and I can't even get that right.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:29.53,0:10:33.42,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我显然已经“伤害”了紫晶的“感情”，\N{\fnArial\fs48}I have apparently "hurt" Amethyst's "feelings",
Dialogue: 100,0:10:33.57,0:10:34.89,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}而这不是我的本意\N{\fnArial\fs48}which was not my intent.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:35.37,0:10:37.76,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}如果我损害了我和这里最出色的宝石人的关系\N{\fnArial\fs48}If I've damaged my standing with the best gem here,
Dialogue: 100,0:10:38.08,0:10:39.84,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}那我犯了一个严重的错误\N{\fnArial\fs48}then I've made a serious mistake.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:40.33,0:10:41.50,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我仍然在学习\N{\fnArial\fs48}I'm still learning.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:42.11,0:10:43.50,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我希望你们能理解\N{\fnArial\fs48}I hope you understand.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:43.86,0:10:45.35,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我希望自己能学会\N{\fnArial\fs48}I want to understand.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:46.20,0:10:47.04,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我很抱歉\N{\fnArial\fs48}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:49.13,0:10:51.64,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}橄榄石，切面五，结束记录\N{\fnArial\fs48}Peridot, facet five. End log.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:52.77,0:10:53.75,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}正如你所见-\N{\fnArial\fs48}As you can see --
